➜浙矿重工亮相宝马展并与国机重工签署战略合作意向书
http://www.sohu.com/a/434450454_237556	22645
<p align="center" style="text-align: left;"><strong><span>2020</span></strong><strong>年<span>11</span>月<span>24</span>日</strong></p>
